{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be sophisticated and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Redstone Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #a30000; /* Deep Red */\n            --secondary-color: #e0a0a0; /* Light muted red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */\n            --font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: var(--font-family);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid, .about-section, .contact-section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #3a3a3a;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 6px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .about-content p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            opacity: 0.95;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 1.5rem);\n            padding: 0.75rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: #3a3a3a;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            outline: none;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input:focus,\n        .contact-form textarea:focus {\n            border-color: var(--primary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(163, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 2rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #c0392b; /* Slightly lighter red for hover */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n                padding: 1.5rem;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Redstone Financial Consulting</h1>\n        <p>Strategic Guidance for Financial Success</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"about-section\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>At Redstone Financial Consulting, we specialize in providing bespoke financial strategies tailored to meet the unique needs of our clients. With a deep understanding of market dynamics and a commitment to integrity, we empower businesses and individuals to achieve their financial goals.</p>\n                <p>Our team of seasoned experts offers comprehensive analysis, prudent advice, and actionable solutions to navigate the complexities of modern finance.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"services-section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Investment Management</h3>\n                    <p>Strategic planning and execution for optimal portfolio growth.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Financial Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive roadmaps for long-term financial security and wealth accumulation.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>\n                    <p>Identifying and mitigating potential financial risks for robust stability.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Corporate Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Expert guidance on mergers, acquisitions, and capital structuring.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"contact-section\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                    <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                    <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                    <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Redstone Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}